item.title: CVE-2023-5943|2024-10-18T14:18:45.817Z -- unknown -- wp-adv-quiz
item.description: The Wp-Adv-Quiz WordPress plugin before 1.0.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when unfiltered_html is disallowed.
